Remote Work in the Ninth District

Sidebar

Remote work increased substantially after the COVID-19 pandemic began in 2020. This dashboard captures different aspects of the remote workforce in the states in the Federal Reserve’s Ninth District.

Preparing the dashboard based on the instructions given at Magallanes Reyes (2022), and Aden-Buie et al. (2023).

You can find the code for this dashboard here: https://github.com/hchinander612/Lab01

Column

Univariate Categorical Plot

Numerical Histogram Plot

County Map Plot
